fields.name: HyperX Cloud Alpha Pro
fields.description:
The dual chambers separate the base from the midrange and treble, allowing for optimal adjustments for cleaner, 
softer sounds. The Cloud Alpha headset is a further development on the basis of HyperX with familiar, award-winning comfort thanks to red viscoelastic foam rubber,
 a wider headband and softer, more resilient imitation leather. 
The aluminum frame is designed to ensure that the headset lasts a long time.

fields.name: Logitech G435 Wireless - Blue
fields.description:
WIRELESS LIGHTSPEED
Wireless LIGHTSPEED is only available with Logitech G and allows you to play with high-performance audio response, 
stable connection and long battery life. All with a range of up to 10 m / 33 feet.

fields.name: Logitech G733 Lightspeed Headset
fields.description:
Make it personal. Use free G
HUB game software * to customize lighting and integrate it into the gaming world.
Have fun with about 16.8 million colors, two zones, presets and custom
animations.

fields.name: Razer BlackShark V2
fields.description:
THE SOUND OF ESPORT
If esports means everything to you, then you can give it your all with the Razer BlackShark V2. 
With this esports headset that has three times as great sound as regular headsets, 
superior microphone sharpness and the highest sound insulation, you can play at a professional level.

fields.name: Steelseries Arctis 7+

fields.name: Glorious PC Gaming Race Model O cordless
fields.description:
With its unusual design with holes that reduce weight and contact with the palm for easier grip - even during the sweatiest gaming sessions - Glorious Model O has become a highly sought after mouse on the market.

At 67 grams, it is light and flexible, perfect for those who prefer weight and stability, a mouse that you can move quickly.
The cord is also designed with flexibility in mind, and is light and flexible to prevent it from getting caught during a critical moment.

fields.name: Logitech G PRO Wireless Gaming Mouse
fields.description: Overcomes the limitations of wireless latency with a connection with a reporting frequency of 1 & nbsp; milliseconds.

fields.name: Razer Basilisk V2
fields.description:
Play your way.
Ignore what others say - create your own style of play with the Razer Basilisk V2. Adjust, 
shift and adjust your performance with this highly customizable game mouse, 
to create your very own brand of dominance that will leave traces on the battlefield.

fields.name: Razer Naga Pro
fields.description:
Why specialize in a genre when you can dominate everyone? Adapt to all games with Razer Naga Pro - a wireless mouse that has been upgraded with our latest Razer technology, 
and equipped with three interchangeable side plates for the button layouts you need to master MMO games, 
battle royales and more.

fields.name: SteelSeries Rival 650
fields.description:
Quantum Wireless
The all-new state-of-the-art lag-free system delivers 1,000 Hz, 1 ms latency, 
24-hour battery life and tournament-level frequency hopping for unmatched performance even during the most demanding gaming sessions.

fields.name: Arozzi Verona V2 Gaming Chair
fields.description:
Verona V2 Gaming Chair
Meet Verona v2 where Arozzi takes you to the next level. 
Our Swedish designers have integrated the most popular functions from our other product lines together with the latest in ergonomic design, to produce a gaming chair that places you at the center of control and comfort. 
A soft imitation leather upholstery over a light metal frame gives a luxurious feeling, while the flexibility to move and react quickly has been maintained.

With its new and incredibly comfortable woven fabric, 
this chair offers maximum comfort even during very long gaming sessions. 
It takes care of your back while defeating all your opponents. Sit down, relax and game on!

fields.name: Corsair gaming k95 rgb platinum
fields.description:
Corsair gaming k95 rgb platinum

You asked for everything. Here it is.
Corsair K95 RGB PLATINUM has CHERRY MX Brown key switch backed by a lightweight aluminum frame. 
8 MB profile storage with hardware macro and lighting playback allows profile access independent of external software. 
Take advantage of the 19-zone LightEdge to add dramatic animations and effects.

fields.name: Corsair K70 RGB TKL Mechanical Keyboard
fields.description:
READY TO COMPETE

Equip yourself with the K70 RGB TKL, a competitive level mechanical gaming keyboard with a portable thinkyless form factor, 
a durable aluminum frame and a tournament mode switch, for quick combat readiness.

fields.name: Logitec g915 tkl tactile
fields.description:
Logitech-G915-TKL-Tactile

A breakthrough in design and technology, now in black and white shades. G915 TKL has LIGHTSPEED, wireless connection in professional class, 
advanced LIGHTSYNC RGB and high-performance mechanical switches with low profile. 
G915 TKL is carefully made of high quality materials and has a sophisticated design that is incredible when it comes to appearance, 
strength and performance. Now in an even more compact form factor. G915 TKL. Play the next dimension.

fields.name: Logitech G513 Carbon RGB (GX Brown Tactile Switch)
fields.description:
A significant advantage
G513 is a high-performance gaming keyboard with a reporting frequency of 1 ms and a choice between the advanced, 
mechanical switches Romer-G Tactile or Romer-G Linear. A full RGB spectrum combined with LIGHTSYNC technology takes the lighting experience of your games to a whole new level. 
Aluminum alloy gives a leaf-shaped chassis with a beautiful brushed metal surface.

fields.name: Svive Triton RGB Mini 60 (Speed)
fields.description:
Svive Triton Mini is just the right keyboard for all minimalist gamers out there. 
This keyboard is equipped with linear speed switches and gives you the fastest response rate. 
Its 60% 62-key Nordic layout and practical design make it a perfect complement to your set at home or when you're on the go, 
and give you a neat and organized desk wherever you are.

fields.name: Varmilo VA109M Cherry MX Red - Panda
fields.description:
armilo VA109 Panda MX Red

Varmilo is the keyboard manufacturer from Taiwan that takes quality very seriously. With key caps in PBT plastic (Polybutene terephthalate) and MX Cherry-Red which gives a premium feeling to the user. 
The keyboards also have function keys that allow you to easily access functions such as increase / decrease volume when playing.

The keyboards from Varmilo are equipped with 5 robust rubber cushions and 2 rubber feet that make it stand firm during the game session.
